OL,5,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FIn Rotherham's A&E a patient with
OL,7,     Fa suspected head injury is under
OL,8,     Farrest in the car park. In London,
OL,9,     Fan eye injury from mixing concrete
OL,10,     Frequires action to prevent
OL,11,     Fpermanent damage.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FA 62-year-old finance broker
OL,14,     Ffights for his life after he
OL,15,     Fsuffers a cardiac arrest while out
OL,16,     Fjogging. A 32-year-old labourer is
OL,17,     Fstabbed in the neck and abdomen
OL,18,     Foutside his home.
