OL,5,G0100 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FDr Zareena Hyder is concerned
OL,7,     Fabout a patient who's lost two
OL,8,     Fstone in six weeks, and is keen to
OL,9,     Frule out cancer. Plus, balancing
OL,10,     Fpain medication, and an alarming
OL,11,     Fasthma flare-up.
OL,12,G0200 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,13,     FBarnsley Casualty is facing one of
OL,14,     Fits toughest shifts to date. With
OL,15,     Fno children's beds available
OL,16,     Facross the whole of Yorkshire, and
OL,17,     Fa department filling up with
OL,18,     Fchildren.
